# Agent tools

Target shape: `AgentTool` from `pi-agent-core` (see `docs/architecture.md`). Legacy CLI extensions in `_template` use `PiApi.registerTool` — migrate to SDK exports.

Patterns (from `dotfiles/phase-loop-pi/extensions/phase-loop-tools.ts`):

- TypeBox schemas for parameters
- `execFile`/`spawn` — never `shell: true`
- Timeouts, `maxBuffer`, secret redaction
- Export pure helpers for unit tests
- Loop-level `beforeToolCall` for governance when wired through `runtime/`

Third-party tools: `tools/vendor/` adapters + registry allowlist — `docs/third-party-extensions.md`.
